property.value: You're not going to survive that jump just like that. But there is a ~cave~ nearby. You'll find what you need there.

properties.property: So, you have awakened. You can't remember anything, do you?
You found the ~Sacred Gloves~! |Your body feels much stronger all of a sudden.

property.name: text
property.value: If you want to get off the island, you need to pass the ~Cave of Trials~.|This will help you.

properties.property: You're on an island called ~The Sanctuary~.|..hm?|We're not the ~Ancients~, but I get the confusion... We're decendants of them, if you will.
You've entered the ~Cave of Trials~.|The only way off this island is through here. ~Your test begins now~.|Good luck.

property.name: text
property.value: This island was once part of the main land.|It has been separated from the world in order to ~protect the Ancients' legacy~.
